high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the oven, then hang a right and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the furthest spatula off of the counter next to the sink.
Walk over to the stove.
Put the spatula handle up in the metal pan that is on the back left burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pan with the spatula in it off of the stove.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Put the metal pan with the spatula in it on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal pan with a spatula in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go forward toward the counter, then turn right to go to the sink.
Pick up the spatula on the counter, nearest to the wall.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to face the stove.
Put the spatula on the pan on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the pan from the left side of the stove.
Turn around and go forward, then turn left toward the counter with the dishwasher beneath it.
Put the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spatula in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your left, take a few steps, turn right and go to the sink
Pick up the kitchen tool/spoon from the counter end to the right of the sink
Turn around and go to the stove
Put the tool/spoon on the pan on rear left side of the stove
Pick up the pan with the spoon
Turn right, turn to your again, move a few steps forward, turn left, and go to the cabinet counter
Place the pan with spoon on the top of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with kitchen spoon on the cabinet top
